    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/64332eab915b553fc0af41447b2f3f77.webp?t=1738352633\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br>游戏现已支持本地双人联机，你可以和自己的朋友共同在异世界进行冒险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/80cb26c39082fba07db51a868c737fc9.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/80cb26c39082fba07db51a868c737fc9.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/80cb26c39082fba07db51a868c737fc9.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/fc427f47dbbad18b68bcca3dfb3cd69b.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/fc427f47dbbad18b68bcca3dfb3cd69b.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/fc427f47dbbad18b68bcca3dfb3cd69b.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/b07b8b0491012be4cd042cb25f40685d.webp?t=1738352633\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/051277f1d79ea72a5ea39a2ff05baac3.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/051277f1d79ea72a5ea39a2ff05baac3.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/051277f1d79ea72a5ea39a2ff05baac3.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏共有九种职业可供选择：战士、圣骑士、锤兵、黑卫士、游侠、巫师、野蛮人、牧师及盗贼。<br>每个职业拥有独特的攻击机制，不同职业彼此之间的配合可以造成专属进攻效果。<br>你可以和自己的小伙伴利用职业和装备加成，打造属于你们的终极团队，去挑战各式各样的boss，梦回童年和小伙伴们一起刷地下城与勇士（DNF）的感觉。<br>在游戏中你可以通过击败敌人来获取不同的道具或者武器装备，同时搭配不同的职业构筑出独特的战斗风格。游戏中道具与武器共有近百种，你可以构筑出无数种组合<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/b27b38ac55ce3a7e62da3cc30c8a8a27.webp?t=1738352633\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/e7e439941290e953b922b25bd08bd58b.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/e7e439941290e953b922b25bd08bd58b.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/e7e439941290e953b922b25bd08bd58b.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/c57bf6afa519abc5d1d6afcb57026d7b.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/c57bf6afa519abc5d1d6afcb57026d7b.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/c57bf6afa519abc5d1d6afcb57026d7b.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/0561c549a32038c16866883e208727fa.webp?t=1738352633\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><br>在这场冒险旅途中，数十种强大的怪物boss正在等待着你们的讨伐。这些怪物强大且拥有精湛的战斗技巧以及独特的攻击机制，注定每一场战斗都将紧张刺激。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/ab2af0b426044cc56a24e3ef24c03c88.poster.avif?t=1738352633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/ab2af0b426044cc56a24e3ef24c03c88.webm?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164240/extras/ab2af0b426044cc56a24e3ef24c03c88.mp4?t=1738352633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，这些强大的boss拥有类似怪物猎人的特殊弱点机制。",
